snippet.title: Blue-Collar Astronaut gives you the skills you need for space-tomorrow
snippet.description:
2D physics space flight meets your student loans in Blue-Collar Astronaut coming out March 14th for PS3/4/Vita, Wii U, Steam (PC/Mac/Linux), and Xbox One!

Find out more at http://blue-collarastronaut.com/
